Artificial Intelligence
How can industry leaders design the principles and technical standards into their products that benefit society as a whole? Vista CEO Robert Smith leads a panel on this question with IBM CEO Ginni Rometty, Microsoft CEO Satya Nadella, MIT Media Lab Director Joichi Ito, and HealthTap CEO Ron Gutman at the World Economic Forum.                                         Watch the Video







                                         
                                    
                                    

Smith: Job Skills Will Be the Next Generation Challenge
Robert Smith, founder and chief executive officer at Vista Equity Partners, discusses using technology to solve society's problems and the challenge of bringing skills and jobs to the next generation. He speaks from the World Economic Forum in Davos, Switzerland on "Bloomberg Surveillance."                                         Watch the Video







                                         
                                    
                                    

