								Approach								

								
															
								Vista Consulting Group							
															
							





















			OVERVIEW		

Vista Consulting Group (VCG) is a team of subject matter experts who work in conjunction with portfolio company executives and Vista investment professionals to help our businesses strengthen their operations through standardized and repeatable processes and methodologies. Vista Best Practices are what sets VCG apart within the industry, and continue to be developed and refined, year after year.
VCG is dedicated to providing multiple points of leverage to support our portfolio companies. We are actively involved in providing support across the existing portfolio, and we serve as the immediate source of expertise for our new investments.
For additional information, meet our team or contact us.













				VCG is a group of high energy, passionate people that are very focused on helping our companies grow, helping our companies solve problems, and the challenges that are in front of them.
				





				–Phil Cunningham, Advicent Solutions
			






What We Do






Thought Leadership
Implementing and Developing Vista Best Practices







Value Creation
Access to Enterprise-Class Tools and Analytics







Peer to Peer Sharing
Facilitating Knowledge Transfer







Executive Development
Recruiting and Developing Talent



 

Who we are 





Subject Matter Experts

                            Experienced executives that partner to create immediate and long-term value                        





                        Vista has expertise in subjects such as business applications, finance / G&A, corporate development, talent, product and technology, marketing, sales, and customer operations                    







Strategic Guides

                            Consulting leaders that work with company executives to develop and implement strategies to unlock value                        





                        Vista drives immediate effectiveness of best practices by working with executives to plan and prioritize key value creating initiatives, creating foundational cornerstone projects that reach across portfolio, and assisting with company level hiring and activity                    







Third Party Relationship Management

                            Vendor consolidation and combined purchasing power creates economies of scale and access to best in breed providers for the portfolio                        





                        Vista helps harness synergies by identifying purchasing trends, products, and service commonalities, improving end-to-end sourcing, offering preferred vendor relations across the portfolio creates consistent methodologies and beneficial consistency, and providing specialized services for niche needs                    






























